                    <h5 class="restaurant">Health & Taste Restaurant</h5><br>
                    <p>Name: <%= name%></p><br>
                    <p>Reservation Number: <%= id%></p> <br>
                    <p class="lineReservation">Thank you for your reservation. You are safe to close this window</p><br>
                    <p>Due to issues with email providers you wont recieve the email for now, to change your reservation save your reservation number and click the link below:</p><br>
                    <p>https://health-and-taste.up.railway.app/edit</p>
                    <button><a href="/">Done!</a></button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </body>
